NOTICE UNDER MECHANIC'S LIEN LAW
TO THE SCHOHARIE COUNTY CLERK IN NEW YORK STATE,
MAXWELL B. STRYKER, JR. AND ALL OTHERS WHOM IT MAY
antrag
CONCERN:
PLEASE TAKE NOTICE, Casco Contracting Corp. has and claims a lien as
stated below for the agreed price and reasonable value of the materials and services
Cm . fordica
rendered as hereafter mentioned in this Lien. This Lien is claimed under the New York
State Lien Law upon the real property described below for the improvements described
below.
1.
Lienor is a domestic corporation whose business address and principal
place of business is PO Box 817 Suffern, New York 10901.
2.
Monaco Cooper Lamme & Carr PLLC, 1881 Western Avenue, in Albany
New York 12203 are the lienor's attorneys.
3.
The owner of the real property against whose interest a lien is claims is
Maxwell B. Stryker, Jr. with an address of 342 Brimstone Church Road, Stamford, New
York.
4.
Upon information and belief the interest of the owner as far as known to
the lienor is owner in fee simple.
5.
The owners and the lienor entered into a contract for work to be
performed and materials to be furnished on or about January 22, 2201. The original
contract totaled $51,912.00.
